### Create Conversation
POST http://localhost:9503/api/conversations

###

### List Conversations
GET http://localhost:9503/api/conversations

###

### Send Message (replace {id} with actual conversation ID)
POST http://localhost:9503/api/conversations/{id}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello, this is a new conversation"
}

###

### Delete Conversation
DELETE http://localhost:9503/api/conversations/{id}
